STIMscope
=========

STIMscope = Spatio-Temporal Illumination Microscope (Aharoni Lab, UCLA
Department of Neurology). This containerized distribution is maintained
internally as CRISPI (Closed-Loop Real-Time Imaging and Stimulation
Pipeline Infrastructure).

