Third-party libraries
------------------------------------------------------------------------
Listed in requirements.txt (pinned) and pulled at Docker image build
time. Each dependency is governed by its own license, which can be
inspected via `pip show <package>` inside the container.

The platform also requires the IDS Peak SDK (proprietary, IDS Imaging
Development Systems GmbH) at runtime for hardware mode; the .deb
installer is NOT redistributed and must be downloaded separately by
the operator (see README for instructions).

The DLPC3479 / DLP4710 DMD controller protocol used by the projector
engine follows the public TI DLPU081A datasheet.
